{"tid":2213674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜講鬼故時間--------大家一齊傾下撞鬼經歷","createTime":"2020-09-22T16:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T21:22:15.000Z","uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd142a094d36503f855beb2d01d3882382b157e","tid":2213674,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dn98w7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdn98w7E.jpg&h=104b3bbb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我曾經同班朋友半夜12點去過元朗達德學校,<br />\n姐係全香港最猛鬼既荒廢學校....<br />\n<br />\n1.我賣甩左其他朋友,自己一個人行 <br />\n<br />\n2.地下好多積水<br />\n<br />\n3.廁所好污糟, 印像中無鏡,我不斷大力踢開廁格,入面好多垃圾<br />\n<br />\n4.其中一個朋友有陰陽眼,果晚佢面勁青, 個一入到去個頭勁痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.果種陰森難以形容, 好似落左陰間咁<br />\n<br />\n6..間學校好細, 十幾分鐘行完<br />\n<br />\n7.聽聞有保安, 但我地見唔到<br />\n<br />\n8.最陰森係禮堂, 形住形住好多死左既人係果度<br />\n<br />\n9.平生唔信鬼, 但當時都有少少淆.<br />\n<br />\n10.出到操場有番啲月光, 開始冇咁恐怖.<br />\n<br />\n11 陰陽眼朋友事後幾日同我講當晚有野跟我走, 的確果一年幾黑仔,成日病, 但後來回復正常, 可能我讀聖經/返教會果陣, 不知不覺驅走左佢."},{"pid":"f9626092a5c0d50feeac5668e4106ef762bce97f","tid":2213674,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"大家有冇撞鬼經歷分享, 唔一定要親身.<br />\n上網聽過/電台/ 朋友經歷都OK"},{"pid":"c81ab3358f31e5bf6e8c09085c15c58933d97e5b","tid":2213674,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b77a9bfa54150f59f445427033f8386fad11281","tid":2213674,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c81ab3358f31e5bf6e8c09085c15c58933d97e5b","tid":2213674,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jLJpCiqL9CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?